Subject: DPI doesn't works with Kaspersky Endpoint Security
Description: When Kaspersky Endpoint Security is active, NEP canÂ´t block access to personal Gmail accounts on MacOS Sequoia 15.2 (24C101).  When Kaspersky Endpoint Security is Off, NEP works Ok.
